{"tid":1316923,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《今晚睇RTHK直播，我老豆變咗黃絲》","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T02:45:40.000Z","uid":269743,"like":1040,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"3800ecfaffcb254348a2e2f58c8674c61040c9d5","tid":1316923,"uid":269743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:01:08.000Z","msg":"一個搬走咗嘅沙田人，遊完行返咗娘家食飯<br />\n返到屋企見到播緊RTHK LIVE<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=我老豆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘩世界末日啊？！竟然唔係睇tvb<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早幾日細佬返咗黎，唔識較返tvb<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咩，我都唔識喎，咁睇住RTHK先啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽樓下啲人講，帶頭盔前面嗰啲個個收哂錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾錢啊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1萬蚊啊，啲工會俾㗎，黎智英去咗美國科水啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想去啊，幫我問下點聯絡丫，我等錢洗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一路食飯，一路播緊譚文豪想同警犬傾，但冇人理佢，一路包抄市民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘩係唔係搞事啊啲警察？！又唔同人傾，究竟想唔想解決件事㗎？肯定想逼到人冇路走又話人衝擊啦，又話人暴徒啦～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係囉～做咩包抄啲人嘅？唔放人走又叫人走嘅？點走啊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲警察真係好仆街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘩啲人掉嘢落啲警察到啊！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾我都掉佢啦～又冇路走，唔掉佢掉邊個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁又係&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n畫面一轉，幾隻狗狂揼兩條友，記者趕到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘩，當人殺父仇人咁打嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘩呢個普通衫，冇口罩，冇安全帽，分分鐘街坊黎，好慘啊<br />\n<br />\n畫面再入新城市入面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘩唔係阿嘛&hellip;咁都得？！見人就打<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不嬲都係咁㗎啦～你啱啱戒tvb係有啲唔慣㗎喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘩呢度得3個警察咋！快啲圍住佢黎打啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有見地！<br />\n<br />\n我呆咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上面有省略咗，仲上咗好多公民教育堂嘅其實<br />\n<br />\n結論係<br />\n遠離tvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只需幾日就有效果"},{"pid":"059d02985b18f5acace1c6679a5d09d5b1f51a4b","tid":1316923,"uid":238051,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">你扮警察\n有人冒警\n我冇嘢講\n我要搵律師</code></pre>"},{"pid":"d18aac4a10405b968466a6564ee09d0398b8d57d","tid":1316923,"uid":63350,"like":59,"dislike":3,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:07:54.000Z","msg":"向伯友致敬"},{"pid":"0211b6ae2ea28a76e5247f9d32d4485a33c28fc2","tid":1316923,"uid":24961,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:09:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"582b128469321685b4135a5ad9af2152319f7608","tid":1316923,"uid":269743,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdaHZZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdaHZZP.jpg&h=9dfe6bee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee75058f1249d21716d976653d84c115e22aee09","tid":1316923,"uid":153239,"like":107,"dislike":0,"score":107,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:10:45.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">嘩呢度得3個警察咋！快啲圍住佢黎打啦！</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be20bd91c5a6830089705ccc86ac0bec9df977fc","tid":1316923,"uid":33736,"like":159